title: Dark Sewer (Horror)
briefDescription: Hello everyone! This is the first time I've ever made a map. This is a horror map. The storyline is simple: you're lost in the ...

crawledImageUrls.text:
Hello everyone! This is the first time I?ve ever made a map. This is a horror map. The storyline is simple: you?re lost in the underground sewer and you have to find a way out.
Mods that I use in this map:
+ Demogorgon https://mcpedl.com/demogorgon-addon/
+ Colored Water https://mcpedl.com/coloredwater-texture-pack/
+ Bicubic Shader
Rule :
+ Brightness 70% ? 100% (don?t turn 1%, you won?t be able to see anything )
+ Sound volume 100%
+ You can play with your friends, but I prefer you play alone.
+ Gamemode: Survival/Adventure (if you?re on Survival, please don?t break any block)
What?s in the game?
Well, this game?s like a maze, you have to find a way out or get stuck here forever. There are several interesting places in the sewer. Hope you would find them.
And also, there are many hidden barrels on the map. They are under the water or in a wall, it?s very hard to see them.
There are two types of the mob that will hunt and attack you in the game: Demogorgon and hostile cod (remember don?t swim in the water too much, they?ll bite you)

Hello how are you, today I bring you my second creation, MODERN HOUSE V2. I uploaded one recently, you can download it too !.
This house is simple and minimalist, last 1 day in just building it, the house has a room with 2 beds, kitchen, dining room and living room. It is two floors and outside it has a pool with several umbrellas to protect you from the sun, you will not be alone because the mods also enjoy a stay in the pool.
The pool has approx. 3 blocks deep and a ladder to get out. Near the house is a river with fascinating aquatic animals such as turtles, octopuses and dolphins.
It has a small dock with 8 boats so you can ride on the river and explore new places.
